descriptionHtml:
this face is young woman style, height 1.0 looks a little weird. It is recommended to set height to 0.7 ~ 0.8 and head to 1.15+, but this will cause the view problem, you can use mod [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/37347/?]Customizable Camera[/url] to solve it.

secondly, default voice is too old for this, such as mod [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/11781/?]Cute Voice 2nd[/url] can solve it.

of course, it is also ok to ignoring these :)

Required mods:
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/]KS Hairdo's renewal[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35327/]SG Female Eyebrows[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/]The Eyes of Beauty[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51602/]Fair Skin Complexion[/url]
